OL,8,     Gmisbehaving? Hetty is determined
OL,9,     Gto find out.
OL,10,G2100FThe Count of Monte Cristo
OL,11,     GEmbedded in Parisian high
OL,12,     Gsociety, the Count methodically
OL,13,     Gdestroys those who betrayed him,
OL,14,     Gonly to discover that vengeance
OL,15,     Gthreatens to consume the innocent
OL,16,     Galong with the guilty.
OL,17,G2150FThe Count of Monte Cristo
OL,18,     GAs his plans reach their end,
OL,19,     GEdmond must choose between
OL,20,     Grevenge and mercy, confronting
OL,21,     Gthe cost of becoming the man he
OL,22,     Gset out to be.
